ps://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75641339_184634683761393_2675350997552393899_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=F4BEG58vZ6kQ7kNvgG14L3z&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAN_tP8AE2H0mM_8mq1VIUacTGDc9KJcJuu2EThf8tpdA&oe=674329D2"}, {"file_name": "SS5.png", "id": "411302063697425", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003249_411302067030758_3628480977844434449_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=lC-qDFxKEaAQ7kNvgGB2hrZ&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYASaTmc29k7yUcTRd4zdI9WkA7aFsEeNjNjq8MFTMC-Zg&oe=6742F835"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "CA_Y.png", "id": "903752467203527", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982530_903752470536860_7264819481473567_n.png?_nc_cat=102&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=tbHXWp3k1u4Q7kNvgFNHeKK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCiAcNlilY6IJTIF961VFV6eeb1mFPsr2S4nLHCWi7Cew&oe=6743112A"}, "display_name": "EC ARMS", "keywords": [], "long_description": "An energy-collecting shooting game.\nYou collect energy from enemies that block your path.\nWe aimed for a feeling of exhilaration when absorbing energy.\nPlease experience the comfort of absorbing energy!\n\n\u2022 Method of operation\nFor hand tracking only.\nThe move is automatic.\nAim to escape from the base with two operations:\n1.Attack mode - Either hand is a Paper\nThe pointer will come out. You can start or attack the enemy by hitting the pointer. Attack and get energy from your enemies.\n2.Absorption mode - Both hands are Paper\nIf there is energy in the scene, it will absorb the energy. Collect a lot of energy.\n(It cannot be absorbed after a certain distance.)\n\n\u2022 How to proceed with the game:\n1.Start\nStart when the gauge of the START icon is full.\n2.GamePlay\nOnce started, the move is automatic. When hit by an enemy bullet, the energy is reduced.\n3.GameOver\nIf you cannot escape by the 